          <div class="space-y-3 text-[#D4D4D4] font-[Public_Sans] leading-relaxed mt-4">
            <p>
              Bonus reviews describe the terms as we understand them at the time of writing. Casino terms change frequently and without notice. Always verify the current terms on the casino's own website before depositing.
            </p>
            <p>
              Gambling carries risk. The house has a mathematical edge on every game. You should only wager funds you are prepared to lose entirely. No strategy, bonus, or system eliminates the house edge.
            </p>
            <p>
              Any mention of potential winnings or bonus values is illustrative. It does not imply that you will achieve similar results. Past bonus availability does not guarantee future availability.
            </p>
            <p>
              We do not provide tax advice. Gambling winnings are taxable in many jurisdictions. Consult a tax professional for guidance on reporting gambling income.
